{"word":"παράφορος","slug":"παράφορος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>παράφορος</b></el> <el>(παράφορος, ον,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>παραφέρομαι</el>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>borne aside, carried away</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>wandering, reeling, staggering</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>mad, frenzied</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}